106
00:07:42,530 --> 00:07:43,270
That is sweet.

107
00:07:43,450 --> 00:07:47,000
But Amber,
I'm kind of saving up for my house.

108
00:07:47,080 --> 00:07:48,740
So, I won't be able to spend much...

109
00:07:49,290 --> 00:07:51,890
Hey, I'm paying for the trip.
You're coming for free!

110
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:52,850
Really?

111
00:07:53,310 --> 00:07:54,880
Las Vegas for free!

112
00:07:55,060 --> 00:07:55,850
Good offer.

113
00:07:56,850 --> 00:07:57,640
But...

114
00:07:59,100 --> 00:08:00,020
But I can't.

115
00:08:00,510 --> 00:08:01,390
I won't be able to make it.

116
00:08:11,100 --> 00:08:11,930
Praf...

117
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:13,520
No way... Not again!

118
00:08:13,890 --> 00:08:16,230
