going to make a mistake!

196
00:11:13,390 --> 00:11:14,930
Yes, I'll make mistakes!

197
00:11:15,890 --> 00:11:17,890
I make mistakes!
But I also agree to making them.

198
00:11:18,100 --> 00:11:21,020
I don't lie to myself like you two.
Look at yourselves.

199
00:11:21,770 --> 00:11:24,410
If this is how married couples behave,
then it's better to be a divorcee.

200
00:11:24,490 --> 00:11:26,230
Get out of my house then!

201
00:11:26,520 --> 00:11:28,430
If we are so bad then
why do you stay with us?

202
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:29,430
Get out of my house!

203
00:11:29,520 --> 00:11:31,140
Don't yell! It will do you more harm.

204
00:11:31,230 --> 00:11:32,680
All because of you!
- You'll get a heart attack.

205
00:11:32,810 --> 00:11:33,350
We have just one daughter!

206
00:11:33,430 --> 00:11:34,770
Just eat the pizza.
- And you couldn't even take care of her.

207
00:11:34,890 --> 00:11:35,520
What have I...

208
00:11:35,640 --> 00:11:37,270
You two have made
my life a living hell.

209
00:11:37,350 --> 00:11:39,270
I'd rather be dead.
- Will you stop it and just eat?

210
00:11:39,390 --> 00:11:40,390
This is all because of you.

211
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:41,430
Because of me?

212
00:11:41,560 --> 00:11:42,930
Go! You too go with her.

213
00:11:43,060 --> 00:11:44,890
Yes, I would, but I cannot walk!

214
00:11:45,020 --> 00:11:49,420
