- I should have left you both in Ahmedabad...

215
00:11:49,500 --> 00:11:50,730
Hello, Amber?

216
00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:52,100
Let's go to Vegas.

217
00:12:21,030 --> 00:12:23,310
This is... This is like so big...

218
00:12:23,640 --> 00:12:25,030
